<h2 id="_social_media">1. Social Media</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In this menu, you can save <strong>URLs</strong> for <strong>social media</strong> platforms like Facebook and twitter. Furthermore, you can activate or deactivate the link to social media.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
